 Jobs Per $1 Invested Than Fossil Fuel Or Nuclear Jobs\n</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.heatisonline.org/contentserver/objecthandlers/index.cfm?ID=4637&amp;Method=Full\" target=\"_blank\">Renewable energy promotes US job growth better than investment in fossil fuels\n</a><strong>(RF: Direct source for last?)</strong></li>\n</ul>\nLinks to clean energy jobs? Green Jobs Philly? Idealist? Craigslist? Specific companies?\n\n[Meenal: this doesn\'t say much. OK to remove?] We\'re committed to promoting a cleaner, more sustainable future for the city of Philadelphia. Moreover, we believe in a plan that works for all communities, bringing healthy solutions to large and small businesses, neighborhoods, workers, students, senior citizens, and all Philadelphians interested in a higher quality of living.\n\n[Meenal: this doesn\'t say much. OK to remove?] On this page, you will find links to information and a diverse network of businesses and organizations with a brighter vision for the future. With your support, we believe Philadelphia can become a beacon for the twenty-first century, turning a city plagued by economic troubles into fertile ground for solutions that work for all.\n\n[Meenal: rest of this page should be moved to a post on resources or policy]\n<h4><strong>RESOURCES\nSolar, Batteries and Microgrids</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.energysage.com/solar\">Learn About Solar</a> (Energy Sage SunShot)</li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SOuyZWqhlNU\">How Photovoltaic (PV) Solar Works\n</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=96WqrcK2OmM\">How Solar Thermal (Hot Water) Works\n</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-g49IYTKIkA\">Home Energy Management Systems\n</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.homeedison.com/\">HomeEdison Battery Backup System</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://phys.org/news/2015-03-solarcity-microgrids-tesla-batteries.html\">Tesla Home Battery System</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>C